long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Workspace Unloader is a dynamic browser extension designed to enhance your computer's performance by efficiently managing memory usage. It's tailor-made for users who often work with multiple tab groups in their browser. This extension seamlessly unloads tabs from inactive tab groups, thus freeing up crucial memory resources. Its effectiveness lies in optimizing your browsing experience, especially when you are dealing with numerous tab groups. The interface of Tab Group Unloader is straightforward and user-friendly, making it a breeze to configure and use.
